mods.abstract: One color window card (gold on white) announcing two masters at the Ace with Roy Rogers and The Delta Rhythm Kings at Ace of Clubs on May 19 and Jason D. Williams at Ace of Clubs on May 20. Poster is a make-ready. A make-ready tests the ink and prepares the press for use.
